    "description": "“干完这票就能退休”是每个佣兵的梦想。而你似乎终于得到了幸运女神的垂青：AnCom集团希望你前去回收弗雷斯科公司的专利资产。<br><br>整理装备，准备克隆，你即将踏上一段永远改变太阳系的旅程。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不惜一切代价。争取一线生机。</h2>管理自己的私人武装公司：执行各大集团发布的订单，用自己的血泪与牺牲换取声誉。探索星球基地，秘密实验室以及太空船残骸，寻找全新科技、能力以及其他能够帮助你在行动中一往无前的道具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/6d8f64da06dd56bd6c297c52d0da8477.poster.avif?t=1695218489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/6d8f64da06dd56bd6c297c52d0da8477.webm?t=1695218489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/6d8f64da06dd56bd6c297c52d0da8477.mp4?t=1695218489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人无完人。失败是成功之母。</h2>记住你拥有着独一无二的优势：你可以克隆最优秀的员工，并派遣克隆体前去执行刺探敌方弱点的自杀行动。没必要用宝贵的人力资源冒险，谁也不希望看见自己的私人武装公司承担法律责任，毕竟没有人在乎克隆体的死活。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/ab411fd62af8bc174405a98ecef5f088.poster.avif?t=1695218489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/ab411fd62af8bc174405a98ecef5f088.webm?t=1695218489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/ab411fd62af8bc174405a98ecef5f088.mp4?t=1695218489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >绝不要掉以轻心。</h2>其他企业会雇佣心狠手辣的佣兵来执行见不得人的勾当。但是在恶魔的力量面前，人类的本性与进化只会沦为玩物。 <br>召集起一支专业队伍，时刻管理自己的装备与弹药情况，谁也不知道这场太空屠杀中会出现什么样的可怕遭遇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/0a2b9b68190f324bc4718b08bb8114a6.poster.avif?t=1695218489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/0a2b9b68190f324bc4718b08bb8114a6.webm?t=1695218489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347110/extras/0a2b9b68190f324bc4718b08bb8114a6.mp4?t=1695218489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
